item.title: Come, Follow Me Notebooks
item.description: 2019 marks a big change in the way that members of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints attend church and study the gospel. With the switch to a 2-hour meeting block, individuals and families have an exciting chance to study more at home. This journal supports your personal or family home-centered plan for gospel learning and worship. In conjunction with Come, Follow Me—For Individuals and Families, weekly gospel study topics are listed.
